des:
Ask for space Facts, and learn about what really matters, like dark matter.

Astro Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Astro Facts" or "Alexa, open Astro Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
